{{Notability|date=June 2018}} {{One source|date=June 2018}} {{Infobox video game |title=Dirt Track Racing 2 |image= |developer = [[Ratbag Games]] |designer = |engine = Difference Engine II |released=September 1, 2002 |modes = [[Single-player]], [[Multiplayer video game|multiplayer]] |platforms = [[Microsoft Windows]] |genre = [[Racing video game|Racing]] }}
'''Dirt Track Racing 2''' ('''''DTR2''''') is a video game by the now defunct [[Ratbag Games]]. It is the third and final game in the dirt track racing series by Ratbag, which includes Dirt Track Racing (DTR), Dirt Track Racing Sprint Cars (DTRSC), and Dirt Track Racing 2 (DTR2).<ref>[https://www.gamespot.com/dirt-track-racing-2/ GameSpot.com: Dirt Track Racing 2]</ref>
==Reception== GameSpot said, "If you've never played any Ratbag games and are looking for a solid racer with an unusual subject, Dirt Track Racing 2 is well worth trying out." They awarded the game a score of 7.1 (Good).<ref>[https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/dirt-track-racing-2-review/1900-2881381/ PC review at Gamespot.com]</ref>
