[[Image:Fukuwarai-maleface.svg|right|245px|thumb|A game ready to be played, simply print and cut out the face parts to begin.]] '''''Fukuwarai''''' ([[wikt:福|福]][[wikt:笑|笑]][[wikt:い|い]]), or in [[English language|English]], "Lucky Laugh", is a Japanese game played around the [[Japanese New Year|Lunar New Year]]. The game is usually played by children, but adults may play also. The game is similar to that of [[Pin the Tail on the Donkey]] except for being performed on a table. The players of Fukuwarai put parts of the face (such as the [[Human eye|eyes]], [[Eyebrow|eyebrows]], [[Human nose|nose]] and [[mouth]]) onto a blank face. Recently, there have been computer and online games created to simulate Fukuwarai.
